---
/** Illustrative inbound trajectory — ties to FAQ 8–12 week inflection. */
---
<div class="lp-viz lp-viz--on-dark lp-chart-inbound" data-viz>
  <div class="lp-viz-head">
    <p class="lp-viz-kicker">Signal to watch</p>
    <p class="lp-viz-title">Qualified inbound quality (illustrative)</p>
    <p class="lp-viz-note">
      Many engagements show a sharper slope after roughly 8–12 weeks once positioning and narrative align — your baseline varies.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="lp-viz-surface" role="img" aria-label="Line chart: index rises gradually then steepens after week 10">
    <svg class="lp-viz-svg" viewBox="0 0 560 200" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid meet">
      <defs>
        <linearGradient id="lp-inbound-fill" x1="0" y1="0" x2="0" y2="1">
          <stop offset="0%" stop-color="rgba(94, 164, 252, 0.35)"></stop>
          <stop offset="100%" stop-color="rgba(94, 164, 252, 0)"></stop>
        </linearGradient>
      </defs>
      <g class="lp-viz-grid" stroke="rgba(255,255,255,0.08)" stroke-width="1">
        <line x1="48" y1="40" x2="520" y2="40"></line>
        <line x1="48" y1="88" x2="520" y2="88"></line>
        <line x1="48" y1="136" x2="520" y2="136"></line>
        <line x1="48" y1="168" x2="520" y2="168"></line>
      </g>
      <text x="52" y="192" fill="rgba(232,234,237,0.45)" font-size="11" font-family="system-ui,sans-serif">0</text>
      <text x="200" y="192" fill="rgba(232,234,237,0.45)" font-size="11" font-family="system-ui,sans-serif">4 wk</text>
      <text x="312" y="192" fill="rgba(232,234,237,0.45)" font-size="11" font-family="system-ui,sans-serif">8</text>
      <text x="400" y="192" fill="rgba(147,197,253,0.9)" font-size="11" font-weight="600" font-family="system-ui,sans-serif">10–12</text>
      <text x="492" y="192" fill="rgba(232,234,237,0.45)" font-size="11" font-family="system-ui,sans-serif">16 wk</text>
      <line
        class="lp-viz-marker-line"
        x1="392"
        y1="32"
        x2="392"
        y2="168"
        stroke="rgba(147,197,253,0.45)"
        stroke-width="1"
        stroke-dasharray="4 4"></line>
      <path
        class="lp-viz-area"
        fill="url(#lp-inbound-fill)"
        d="M 48 158 L 120 152 L 200 146 L 280 128 L 360 88 L 440 58 L 520 42 L 520 168 L 48 168 Z"></path>
      <path
        class="lp-viz-line"
        fill="none"
        stroke="#5ea4fc"
        stroke-width="2.5"
        stroke-linecap="round"
        stroke-linejoin="round"
        d="M 48 158 L 120 152 L 200 146 L 280 128 L 360 88 L 440 58 L 520 42"></path>
    </svg>
  </div>
</div>
